     <div class="accordion faqs-valntioner" id="accordionExample1">
        <div class="card active box-container1">
       <div class="card-header" id="headingOne1">
         <h2 class="mb-0">
           <button type="button" class="btn btn-link" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne1"><i class="fa fa-plus"></i>What kind of CSR activities does MBRDI support?</button>
         </h2>
       </div>
       <div id="collapseOne1" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne1" data-parent="#accordionExample1">
         <div class="card-body">
           <p>CSR at MBRDI is focused on three areas: sustainable mobility, environmental sustainability, and need-based projects.</p>
         </div>
       </div>
     </div>
     <div class="card box-container1">
       <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo2">
         <h2 class="mb-0">
           <button type="button" class="btn btn-link " data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo2"><i class="fa fa-plus"></i>What types of volunteer activities does MBRDI typically engage in?</button>
         </h2>
       </div>
       <div id="collapseTwo2" class="collapse " aria-labelledby="headingTwo2" data-parent="#accordionExample1">
         <div class="card-body">
           <p>Within the focus areas, we typically engage in road safety activities at government schools, biodiversity conservation through plantation and awareness drives, and need-based mentoring programs for persons with disabilities, amongst others. Click <a href="main-events.html">here</a> to see the available volunteering opportunities and those that have been completed.</p>
         </div>
       </div>
     </div>
     <div class="card box-container1">
       <div class="card-header" id="headingThree3">
         <h2 class="mb-0">
           <button type="button" class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree3"><i class="fa fa-plus"></i>How can I get updates on upcoming volunteering opportunities and events?</button>
         </h2>
       </div>
       <div id="collapseThree3" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree3" data-parent="#accordionExample1">
         <div class="card-body">
           <p>You can go to the <a href="main-events.html">“Volunteering Events”</a> page and navigate through the list to find upcoming volunteering opportunities and events.</p>
         </div>
       </div>
     </div>  
     <div class="card box-container1">
         <div class="card-header" id="headingFour1">
           <h2 class="mb-0">
             <button type="button" class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFour1"><i class="fa fa-plus"></i>Who do I reach out to regarding volunteering opportunities?</button>
           </h2>
         </div>
         <div id="collapseFour1" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour1" data-parent="#accordionExample1">
           <div class="card-body">
             <p>All departments at MBRDI have designated CSR SPOCs. The SPOC aligns with the core CSR team at MBRDI to understand available opportunities and gather department-level registrations. Please refer to the <a href="/mbrdi/home.html#spocs">Department SPOCs</a> section on the homepage of this site or the <a href="https://social.cloud.corpintra.net/groups/csr-mbrdi" target="_blank">CSR Social Intranet</a> to find information about your department's CSR SPOC.</p>
           </div>
         </div>
       </div>
       
       <div class="card box-container1">
       <div class="card-header" id="headingFive1">
         <h2 class="mb-0">
           <button type="button" class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFive1"><i class="fa fa-plus"></i>Are there specific guidelines or policies for employees who want to volunteer during company time?</button>
         </h2>
       </div>
       <div id="collapseFive1" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive1" data-parent="#accordionExample1">
         <div class="card-body">
           <p>Yes, please refer to the detailed document <a href="guidelines-faqs.html#volunteering">here</a>.</p>
         </div>
       </div>
     </div>
     
     <div class="card box-container1">
       <div class="card-header" id="headingsix1">
         <h2 class="mb-0">
           <button type="button" class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapsesix1"><i class="fa fa-plus"></i>Are there any recognition programs for employees who participate in volunteering?</button>
         </h2>
       </div>
       <div id="collapsesix1" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingsix1" data-parent="#accordionExample1">
         <div class="card-body">
           <p>All volunteers will receive participation certificates for each CSR activity they volunteer for. Activities and consolidated certificates can be found in your <a href="profile.html">profile section</a>.</p>
         </div>
       </div>
     </div>
     
     <div class="card box-container1">
       <div class="card-header" id="headingseven1">
         <h2 class="mb-0">
           <button type="button" class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseseven1"><i class="fa fa-plus"></i>How can I report my volunteer hours?</button>
         </h2>
       </div>
       <div id="collapseseven1" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingseven1" data-parent="#accordionExample1">
         <div class="card-body">
           <p>You can report your volunteer hours by scanning the QR code shared after an event and filling in the details. Consolidated hours can be found in the <a href="profile.html">“My Profile”</a> section.</p>
         </div>
       </div>
     </div>
     
     <div class="card box-container1">
       <div class="card-header" id="headingEight1">
         <h2 class="mb-0">
           <button type="button" class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseEight1"><i class="fa fa-plus"></i>Do I need approval from my supervisor or manager to participate in volunteering?</button>
         </h2>
       </div>
       <div id="collapseEight1" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingEight1" data-parent="#accordionExample1">
         <div class="card-body">
           <p>Yes. Please ensure participation in all CSR activities is notified to your immediate manager and does not disrupt business requirements or commitments.</p>
         </div>
       </div>
     </div>
     
     <div class="card box-container1">
       <div class="card-header" id="headingNine1">
         <h2 class="mb-0">
           <button type="button" class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseNine1"><i class="fa fa-plus"></i>Can I organize department-specific volunteering activities?</button>
         </h2>
       </div>
       <div id="collapseNine1" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingNine1" data-parent="#accordionExample1">
         <div class="card-body">
          <p>Yes. You can connect with your department's CSR SPOC and get in touch with us at <a href="mailto:csr-mbrdi@mercedes-benz.com">csr-mbrdi@mercedes-benz.com</a> with the requirements. We recommend informing us a month in advance to prepare for the event.</p>
         </div>
       </div>
     </div>
     
     <div class="card box-container1">
       <div class="card-header" id="headingTen1">
         <h2 class="mb-0">
           <button type="button" class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTen1"><i class="fa fa-plus"></i>How can I provide feedback or suggest new volunteer initiatives for MBRDI?</button>
         </h2>
       </div>
       <div id="collapseTen1" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTen1" data-parent="#accordionExample1">
         <div class="card-body">
          <p>You can provide feedback or suggest new volunteer initiatives by using the feedback link that is generated once you have participated in an event. You can also write to us at <a href="mailto:csr-mbrdi@mercedes-benz.com">csr-mbrdi@mercedes-benz.com</a>.</p>
         </div>
       </div>
     </div>
       
       
